                <h1>Discover the Legacy of Frank Woolworth: Retail Innovator</h1>
                <p>Frank Woolworth was a visionary entrepreneur who revolutionized retail in the early 20th century. He founded the "five-and-dime" stores, which offered affordable merchandise, appealing to the everyday consumer. Woolworth's innovative approach laid the groundwork for modern discount retailing, significantly impacting shopping culture and business practices.</p>
